# CLOCK::GET_CLOCK_HOURS

## Summary
Gets the current number of hours on the clock

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the current ingame hour, expressed without zeros. (09:34 will be represented as 9)
